						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up on the lake-bund close to the village.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription may be assigned to the 18th century, on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It states the construction of a tank by Rāja Kāverrāja Bahadūr at the instance of <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Kaṭāri Sāḷva Bommarāju Bahadur. (cf. No. 495).</p>						

						</summary>
